OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FGrenfell Tower: Official   
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fadmits he could have       
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fprevented fire             
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A civil servant has admitted he could  
OL,6, have potentially prevented the Grenfell
OL,7, Tower fire on a number of occasions.   
OL,9,FBrian Martin, the head of technical    
OL,10,Fpolicy for building regulation, told   
OL,11,Fthe public inquiry that he found it    
OL,12,Fhard to express how sorry he was.      
OL,14,FMr Martin was questioned about warnings
OL,15,Fhe was given that the building         
OL,16,Findustry, confused by government       
OL,17,Fguidance, was using dangerous cladding.
OL,19,FHe admitted not realising the severity 
OL,20,Fof the risk at the time.               
